[{"id":"9944e09ba2237ca3e2179f289ef5106a","from":"image32","from_email":"info@image32.com","to":"jeffrey","to_list":[{"name":"jeffrey","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"image32 product update - New folders feature","date":"2014-10-16T22:15:14.000Z","formatted_date":"Oct 16, 2014","formatted_time":"10:15 PM","body":"https://www.image32.com\n\nMany customers have asked for it, and this week we've released our new folders feature. Folders allow you to organize your medical images and share them more easily. The folders can be found on the left side of your image32 screen.\n\nTo create your first folder, move your mouse over the \"My Folders\" header and click the \"add\" link. Once you've set up your folder, you can upload medical images as well as other files, and share the whole folder with one person at a time, or use our new \"Groups\" feature to share with a pre-made group of people.\nRequest a Demo (https://www.image32.com/Product/RequestDemo)\n\nFor those of you who use the Uploader Application, please get the latest here (https://www.image32.com/Download/All) . We've made some updates to improve performance and stability.\n\nThanks for all of your support,\nBob Pellican\nCo-founder and CEO,\nimage32\n\nFollow us:\nhttps://www.facebook.com/image32\nhttps://twitter.com/image32\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/company/image32\nhttps://plus.google.com/+Image32\nhttps://www.youtube.com/user/imagethirtytwo\n\nCopyright \u00a9 2013 Interconnect Medical, Inc. All rights reserved.\n\nThis email was sent to jeeproject@yahoo.com (mailto:jeeproject@yahoo.com)\nwhy did I get this? (http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/about?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=4c2c2f7b6c&e=d239b5474d&c=416d79c578)     unsubscribe from this list (http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/unsubscribe?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=4c2c2f7b6c&e=d239b5474d&c=416d79c578)     update subscription preferences (http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/profile?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=4c2c2f7b6c&e=d239b5474d)\nInterconnect Medical, Inc. \u00b7 1149 Chestnut Street \u00b7 Suite 10 \u00b7 Menlo Park, CA 94025 \u00b7 USA","body_html":"<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\th2{\n\t\t\tmargin-bottom:10px;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp{\n\t\t\tmargin-top:0px;\n\t\t}\n</style><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n\n<body bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\n<table width=\"600px\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center; max-width: 600px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center;\">\n    \t<a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=bb108690a4&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/image32-images/Emails/image32_email_logo.png\" width=\"202\" height=\"88\" border=\"0\"></a>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"vero-editable\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px 40px 20px 40px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: #333333; text-align: left;\"><!-- START CONTENT -->\n      <!-- // Begin Module: Standard Content \\\\ -->\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Many customers have asked for it, and this week we've released our new folders feature. Folders allow you to organize your medical images and share them more easily. The folders can be found on the left side of your image32 screen.</p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Folders</h2>\n      <img src=\"http://storage.googleapis.com/image32-images/Emails/folders_feature.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"186\" alt=\"New Folders Feature\" border=\"0\"> <br>\n      <br>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">To create your first folder, move your mouse over the \"My Folders\" header and click the \"add\" link. \n      Once you've set up your folder, you can upload medical images as well as other files, and share the whole folder with one person at a time, or use our new \"Groups\" feature to share with a pre-made group of people. </p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"padding: 10px 0px 30px 0px; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center;\">\n    \t<a style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;background:#6697D9;padding:10px 15px;border-radius:4px; text-align: center;\" href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=23162c4a56&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\">Request a Demo</a> \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"padding: 0px 40px 20px 40px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: #333333; text-align: left;\">\n    \t<p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">For those of you who use the Uploader Application, please get the latest <a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=dc20189ffb&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>. We've made some updates to improve performance and stability.</p>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Thanks for all of your support,<br>\n        <img src=\"http://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/image32-images/BobPellican_Email_Signature.png\" width=\"140\" height=\"50\" alt=\"Bob Pellican\" border=\"0\"><br>\n        <b>Bob Pellican</b><br>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 10px; line-height: 14px; margin-top: 2px; color: #666666;\">Co-founder and CEO,<br>\n        image32</span> </p>\n      <!-- // End Module: Standard Content \\\\ -->\n      <!-- END CONTENT -->\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\" style=\"padding: 20px 40px 30px 40px; background-color: #EFEFEF; text-align: left;\">\n    \t<p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; margin-top: 2px; color: #666666;\"> \n    \tFollow us: \n      <a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=77737b6686&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://storage.googleapis.com/image32-images/icons_social_media_facebook.png\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" border=\"0\"></a> \n      <a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=97d6290f76&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://storage.googleapis.com/image32-images/icons_social_media_twitter.png\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" border=\"0\"></a> \n      <a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=d3fcfc2895&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://storage.googleapis.com/image32-images/icons_social_media_linkedin.png\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" border=\"0\"></a> \n      <a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=fea1d95a62&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://storage.googleapis.com/image32-images/icons_social_media_google.png\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" border=\"0\"></a> \n      <a href=\"http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=318afa2226&e=d239b5474d\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://storage.googleapis.com/image32-images/icons_social_media_youtube.png\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" border=\"0\"></a> </p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; margin-top: 2px; color: #888888;\"> Copyright &copy; 2013 Interconnect Medical, Inc. All rights reserved. </p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n            <center>\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                <br />\n 